Alpha diversity of RUMEN samples

From 16S rRNA-gene sequencing of cow RUMEN microbiome samples: - 6 treatments for rumen samples + ruminal liquid (base) + (AE1,AE sinttico 1,Carvacrol, p-cymene, -terpinene, no treatment (ruminal liquid + diet))

Correction for baseline

bl_medie <- mAlpha %>%
  filter(treatment=="no treatment (ruminal liquid + diet)") %>%
  group_by(metric) %>%
  summarize(media_bl=mean(value))
  
bl_counts <- mAlpha %>%
  group_by(metric) %>%
  filter(treatment=="no treatment (ruminal liquid + diet)") %>%
  arrange(metric) %>%
  rename(value.bl = value)

M <- merge(mAlpha,bl_counts[,c(1,2,3)],by=c("metric","sample"),all.x = TRUE)
M1 <- M%>%
  filter(!is.na(M$value.bl))

M2 <- M %>%
  filter(is.na(value.bl)) %>%
  mutate(value.bl=replace(value.bl,is.na(value.bl),right_join(bl_medie, ., by =c("metric"))$media_bl))

M <- rbind.data.frame(M1,M2)  

M <- M %>%
  mutate(corrected_counts=value-value.bl) %>%
  filter(value!=0) %>%
  arrange(sample)

M <- M %>%
  group_by(metric) %>%
  mutate(scaled_counts=scales::rescale(corrected_counts,c(0,100)))
